On Debian or Ubunu as the HV os

<hidden state='on'/>
will not work as a workaround for Nvidias Error 43.

For that you need change the XML:

replace first line with:

<domain type='kvm' xmlns:qemu='http://libvirt.org/schemas/domain/qemu/1.0'>

append:

<qemu:commandline>
    <qemu:arg value='-cpu'/>
    <qemu:arg value='host,hv_time,kvm=off,hv_vendor_id=null'/>
  </qemu:commandline>

just before the closing </domain> tag.
